content: "Are you tired of feeling like your coding skills are holding you back? Our upcoming workshop is here to change that! Join us and gain a hands-on understanding of how the new MDM table applies to ED coding and hospital observation and inpatient coding. Learn practical tips and strategies that you can apply in your day-to-day coding and see the results for yourself. Don't miss out on this opportunity to transform your coding career and take control of your future. Register now and let us guide you to success! #EandM #Coding #MDMtable"
